gree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020167d1da8054087f37c650f3ba89918be695c2","tid":87734,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"D客成日話過完年手頭鬆動啲先再講，心諗你係無錢成年都冇錢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ab87f95e94bee12a6865c5f0465cde341e5e46","tid":87734,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁撚叻就唔使做服務業啦<br />\n<br />\n後悔點解當日唔讀好書啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"720666fdf30a7ff9bf82b744a48ef2a11e7b513b","tid":87734,"uid":46858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你咁撚叻就唔使做服務業啦<br />\n<br />\n後悔點解當日唔讀好書啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n冇我地你地自助啦 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇客你返屋企糧地啦 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n咁你去買衫自己去試自己入倉拎貨囉 <br />\n做到我就收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}